API: api-s.sp.kingdomhearts.com
Japanese API: http://api.sp.kingdomhearts.jp
Some requests can be sent without authorization, otherwise you need a session cookie/http token

Chat servers: f.cc001.sqex-chat.jp, f.uc001.sqex-chat.jp

Cache server(for images): cache.sqex-bridge.jp
Example link for cache server: http://cache.sqex-bridge.jp/img/9lyUN7o2US

Game files:
Size of game files is about 1-3GB
Files are encrypted using .jpg .png and mp4 formats

Other stuff:
Servers use Nginx, Varnish, Akamai, Fastly
Varnish is only available for BSD, Linux and Unix
Servers might use Amazon Web Services (which is bad btw)
